        <div class="topic-body">
          <h3>R v Brown (1993)</h3>
          <p>Landmark case on consent and criminal law, involving bodily harm in private acts.</p>
          <a href="https://www.bailii.org/uk/cases/UKHL/1993/19.html" target="_blank" class="btn">Read Full Case</a>
        </div>
